# SEO Validation Rules

## File Structure Validation
- Files must be located in the `src/data/` directory
- Only `.yml` or `.yaml` files are processed
- Excluded directories and files:
  - `/components/`
  - `/plans/`
  - `additional-redirects.yml`
  - `call-to-actions.yml`

## Meta Information Requirements
The following properties are required in the `meta_info` section:

### Required Properties
1. `slug` (string, mandatory)
   - Must be unique across all files
   - Cannot be duplicated within the same entity type
   - Used for URL generation

2. `title` (string, mandatory)
   - SEO-friendly title
   - Must be present and non-empty

3. `description` (string, mandatory)
   - Maximum length: 160 characters (including spaces)
   - Must be unique across all files
   - Cannot be empty or undefined
   - Used for meta description tag

### Optional Properties
1. `image` (string)
   - Path to the image file
   - Can be empty string

2. `keywords` (string)
   - SEO keywords
   - Optional field

3. `redirects` (array)
   - Array of redirect URLs
   - Can be empty array
   - Must be an array type if present

## Image Alt Text Requirements
The following sections must have non-empty `image_alt` properties:
- `python_banner.image_alt`
- `community_banner.image_alt`
- `header.image_alt`
- `what_is_4geeks.image_alt`

## Validation Rules
1. YAML Syntax
   - Files must have valid YAML syntax
   - Invalid syntax will cause validation failure

2. Meta Information
   - `meta_info` section must be present
   - All mandatory properties must be present
   - Property types must match their definitions
   - Array properties must be actual arrays

3. Description Uniqueness
   - Descriptions must be unique across all files
   - Duplicate descriptions will cause validation failure

4. Property Type Validation
   - String properties must be strings
   - Array properties must be arrays
   - Optional properties can be null or undefined
   - Mandatory properties cannot be null or undefined

## Error Handling
The validation process will:
1. Fail if any mandatory requirements are not met
2. Warn about missing image alt texts
3. Success message when all validations pass

## Example of Valid Structure
```yml
meta_info:
  slug: "example-slug"
  title: "Example Title"
  description: "Example description under 160 characters"
  image: ""
  keywords: "Example Keywords"
  redirects: []

header:
  image_alt: "example-alt-text"
```
